sentences: William Ray Norwood Jr. (born January 17, 1981), known  professionally as Ray J, is an American singer, songwriter, television personality, actor, and entrepreneur.
In January 2017, he competed in the nineteenth season of the UK reality television programme Celebrity Big Brother.
Early in his life, he moved with his family from McComb, Mississippi to Los Angeles, California, and in 1989 started appearing in television commercials for different companies.
